          solution for the ethereum blockchain.
        </p>
        <p class="text faded mb-4" align="left">
        The technology exists today to allow a whole class of applications to move the majority of their transactions “off chain”. The complexity of understanding and applying state channel techniques is the main barrier to adoption.
        </p>
        <p class="text faded mb-4" align="left">
        <b>At Magmo, we’re working to make state channels more accessible to the Ethereum developer community.</b>
        </p>
        <p class="text faded mb-4" align="left">
